Requirements
============
lua5.2
	sudo apt-get install lua5.2 liblua5.2-dev
wiringPi library
	sudo apt-get install wiringPi
OLED library
	https://github.com/hallard/ArduiPi_OLED
	modify compiler flags for rpi3 at Makefile
		CCFLAGS=-Ofast -mfpu=neon-fp-armv8 -mfloat-abi=hard -march=armv8-a+crc -mtune=cortex-a53
	